  "short_description": "An innovative twist on the extreme sports genre— with a car. Drive with style through Vaporwave motorparks; discover how to coordinate with Echoes (your clones) to rack up Déjà Vu bonus points, and climb the top of the leaderboards. Explore meme-inspired content, maps, and a Eurobeat soundtrack.",
